                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p class="p1">While Furtado hopes the film will expose the experiences of a post-Cold War history that students are often unaware of even though it is also their own history, he also wants students to explore the concept of utopian thinking and art being a force for change.</p>
<p>“My ultimate fantasy is always that these films will leave some lasting impression and provoke some kind of thought,” Furtado said. “That’s really what I expect with any work of art&mdash;the world looks a little bit different after you engage with it.”</p>
                                    </div>

